#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:1
msgid "Manage a resident"
msgstr "Een bewoner beheren"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:4
msgid ""
"Create a resident, record their admission and stay, and enter the Katz "
"assessment."
msgstr ""
"Een bewoner aanmaken, de opname en het verblijf registreren, de Katz-"
"evaluatie invoeren."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:7
msgid ""
"This page describes a resident's complete journey in Resthome: from "
"**creation** to **active stay**, including the **Katz assessment** that "
"governs INAMI billing."
msgstr ""
"Deze pagina beschrijft het volledige traject van een bewoner in Resthome: "
"van de **aanmaak** tot het **actieve verblijf**, via de **Katz-evaluatie** "
"die de RIZIV-facturatie bepaalt."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:9
msgid "Overview"
msgstr "Overzicht"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:19
msgid "Two dates not to confuse"
msgstr "Twee data om niet te verwarren"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:22
msgid "**Stay start date**: when accommodation billing begins (the room)."
msgstr ""
"**Startdatum verblijf**: wanneer de facturatie van het verblijf (de kamer) "
"begint."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:23
msgid ""
"**Admission date**: when the INAMI intervention begins (the flat-rate fee)."
msgstr ""
"**Opnamedatum**: wanneer de RIZIV-tegemoetkoming (het forfait) begint."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:25
msgid "They are often identical, but can differ — Resthome handles both."
msgstr ""
"Vaak zijn ze identiek, maar ze kunnen verschillen — Resthome beheert beide."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:28
msgid "1. Create the resident"
msgstr "1. De bewoner aanmaken"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:30
msgid "Open the **MR/MRS → Residents** application."
msgstr "Open de toepassing **MR/MRS → Bewoners**."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:31
msgid "Click **New**."
msgstr "Klik op **Nieuw**."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:32
msgid ""
"Enter at least: **name**, **date of birth**, **gender**, and the **NISS** "
"(national number) if known."
msgstr ""
"Vul minstens in: **naam**, **geboortedatum**, **geslacht**, en het "
"**rijksregisternummer (NISS)** indien gekend."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:33
msgid "Select the resident's **health insurance fund**."
msgstr "Selecteer de **mutualiteit** van de bewoner."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:34
#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:50
msgid "**Save**."
msgstr "**Sla op**."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:36
msgid "The NISS is required for eHealth"
msgstr "Het NISS is nodig voor eHealth"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:39
msgid ""
"Without a NISS, insurability verification (MDA) and agreements (eAgreement) "
"cannot be sent. You can create the resident without a NISS, but remember to "
"fill it in as soon as possible."
msgstr ""
"Zonder NISS kunnen de verzekerbaarheidscontrole (MDA) en de akkoorden "
"(eAgreement) niet verstuurd worden. U kunt de bewoner zonder NISS aanmaken, "
"maar vul het zo snel mogelijk aan."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:42
msgid "2. Open a stay agreement"
msgstr "2. Een verblijfsovereenkomst openen"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:44
msgid "The **stay** links the resident to a room and triggers billing."
msgstr ""
"Het **verblijf** koppelt de bewoner aan een kamer en start de facturatie."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:46
msgid "On the resident record, open the **Convention** tab."
msgstr "Open op de fiche van de bewoner het tabblad **Overeenkomst**."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:47
msgid "Click **Add a line**."
msgstr "Klik op **Regel toevoegen**."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:48
msgid "Choose the **room** (only available rooms are offered)."
msgstr "Kies de **kamer** (enkel beschikbare kamers worden voorgesteld)."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:49
msgid "Enter the **stay type** (MR or MRS) and the **stay start date**."
msgstr ""
"Geef het **verblijfstype** (ROB of RVT) en de **startdatum verblijf** op."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:52
msgid "The stay is then in the **Draft** state."
msgstr "Het verblijf staat dan in de status **Concept**."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:54
msgid "3. Confirm then start the stay"
msgstr "3. Bevestigen en het verblijf starten"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:56
msgid "The stay goes through two steps:"
msgstr "Het verblijf doorloopt twee stappen:"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:58
msgid ""
"**Confirm** — the stay becomes *Confirmed* (the room is reserved). The "
"**admission date and time** fields appear: fill them in."
msgstr ""
"**Bevestigen** — het verblijf wordt *Bevestigd* (de kamer is gereserveerd). "
"De velden **opnamedatum en -uur** verschijnen: vul ze in."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:59
msgid ""
"**Start Stay** — the stay becomes *In Progress* (the resident is actually "
"present)."
msgstr ""
"**Start Stay (Starten)** — het verblijf wordt *Lopend* (de bewoner is "
"effectief aanwezig)."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:61
msgid "What starting the stay triggers automatically"
msgstr "Wat de start automatisch in gang zet"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:64
msgid "When the stay starts, Resthome:"
msgstr "Bij de start doet Resthome:"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:66
msgid "adds the resident to the open **billing periods**;"
msgstr "de bewoner toevoegen aan de open **facturatieperiodes**;"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:67
msgid ""
"for a resident billed in advance, creates the **first accommodation "
"invoice** for the admission month;"
msgstr ""
"voor een vooraf gefactureerde bewoner de **eerste verblijfsfactuur** van de "
"opnamemaand aanmaken;"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:68
msgid "opens the month's **supplements envelope**;"
msgstr "de **supplementenenveloppe** van de maand openen;"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:69
msgid "creates the **admission eAgreement** (if the NISS is present)."
msgstr "de **eAgreement voor opname** aanmaken (als het NISS aanwezig is)."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:72
msgid "4. Enter the Katz assessment"
msgstr "4. De Katz-evaluatie invoeren"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:74
msgid ""
"The **Katz** category (O, A, B, C, Cd) determines the **INAMI flat-rate "
"fee**."
msgstr "De **Katz**-categorie (O, A, B, C, Cd) bepaalt het **RIZIV-forfait**."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:76
msgid ""
"From the resident record, open **Assessment tools → Katz** (or the **Katz** "
"button)."
msgstr ""
"Open vanaf de fiche van de bewoner **Evaluatietools → Katz** (of de knop "
"**Katz**)."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:77
msgid ""
"Click **New** and score the 6 criteria (washing, dressing, transfer, going "
"to the toilet, continence, eating)."
msgstr ""
"Klik op **Nieuw** en scoor de 6 criteria (wassen, kleden, transfer, toilet, "
"continentie, eten)."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:78
msgid "**Confirm** then **Validate** the assessment."
msgstr "**Bevestig** en **Valideer** de evaluatie."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:80
msgid "No validated Katz?"
msgstr "Geen gevalideerde Katz?"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:83
msgid ""
"As long as no validated Katz exists, the resident is in category **O** by "
"default, and a \"Katz to do\" reminder appears on the dashboard."
msgstr ""
"Zolang er geen gevalideerde Katz bestaat, staat de bewoner standaard in "
"categorie **O**, en verschijnt een herinnering « Katz te doen » op het "
"dashboard."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:86
msgid "5. Check insurability (MDA)"
msgstr "5. De verzekerbaarheid controleren (MDA)"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:88
msgid "Before billing, check that the resident is properly insured:"
msgstr "Controleer vóór het factureren of de bewoner wel verzekerd is:"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:90
msgid "Open the month's billing period, or the resident record."
msgstr "Open de facturatieperiode van de maand, of de fiche van de bewoner."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:91
msgid "Run an **MDA check** (MyCareNet/WalCareNet insurability)."
msgstr "Start een **MDA-controle** (verzekerbaarheid MyCareNet/WalCareNet)."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:92
msgid ""
"Resthome automatically updates the **health insurance fund** and the **BIM**"
" status where applicable."
msgstr ""
"Resthome werkt automatisch de **mutualiteit** en de **BIM**-status bij "
"indien nodig."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:94
msgid "Special cases"
msgstr "Bijzondere gevallen"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:96
msgid ""
"**Room change**: use the dedicated action on the stay — accommodation "
"billing is split across the two rates, without a new admission."
msgstr ""
"**Kamerwissel**: gebruik de speciale actie op het verblijf — de "
"verblijfsfacturatie wordt gesplitst aan beide tarieven, zonder nieuwe "
"opname."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:97
msgid ""
"**MR ↔ MRS transfer**: a wizard records the transfer date and updates the "
"stay type."
msgstr ""
"**Overdracht ROB ↔ RVT**: een assistent registreert de overdrachtsdatum en "
"werkt het verblijfstype bij."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:98
msgid ""
"**Absence / hospitalization**: see the [Billing](../facturation/index.md) "
"section — an absence adjusts the flat-rate fee and can generate an eHealth "
"notification (Annexe 11)."
msgstr ""
"**Afwezigheid / hospitalisatie**: zie de sectie "
"[Facturatie](../facturation/index.md) — de afwezigheid past het forfait aan "
"en kan een eHealth-melding genereren (Bijlage 11)."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:99
msgid ""
"**End of stay / death**: close the stay; Resthome stops billing on the "
"correct date and prepares the credit note if needed."
msgstr ""
"**Einde verblijf / overlijden**: sluit het verblijf af; Resthome stopt de "
"facturatie op de juiste datum en bereidt indien nodig de creditnota voor."

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:101
msgid "Further reading"
msgstr "Verder lezen"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:103
msgid "[Billing](../facturation/index.md)"
msgstr "[Facturatie](../facturation/index.md)"

#: ../../content/residents/gerer-un-resident.md:104
msgid "[eHealth](../ehealth/index.md)"
msgstr "[eHealth](../ehealth/index.md)"
